 "cells": [
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(*计算Δ矩阵元对应的CG系数*)\r\nClebschGordan[{1, 0}, {1, 0}, {2, 0}]\r\n(*根据mma的定义，这里三对系数分别是j1m1,j2m2,jm分别对应两个分角动量和最终的总角动量，和Wigner-Eckart定理的对应是j1m1对应初态目前记为JmJ，j2m2对应秩和投影目前秩是1因为矢量算符，投影是0，±1等于ms-mJ，jm对应末态记为SmS*)",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wexpr\"><wsqrt><w><w>\\</w></w><w></w><w><wfrac><w><w>2</w></w><w><w></w><w><w>3</w></w></w></wfrac></w></wsqrt></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Sqrt[2/3]",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "1be48ac2-a515-4822-9a34-cf7010fafacc",
